# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:10
translate spanish mills1_de9fb575:

    # "As soon as I go into Mrs. Mills office to start working, I know something is wrong."
    "En cuanto entro en la oficina de la Sra. Mills para empezar a trabajar, sé que algo va mal."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:12
translate spanish mills1_46eab517:

    # "Mrs. Mills stands up from her desk and walks up to me as soon as I shut the door."
    "La Sra. Mills se levanta de su escritorio y se acerca a mí en cuanto cierro la puerta."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:13
translate spanish mills1_9720edc3:

    # bs "Look [pcname], you have a lot of work to do today."
    bs "Mira [pcname], hoy tienes mucho trabajo que hacer."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:14
translate spanish mills1_9c04a9df:

    # bs "So I don't want you just jerking off like you have been."
    bs "Así que no quiero que te dediques a perder el tiempo como has estado haciendo."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:15
translate spanish mills1_60630d5f:

    # bs "No sitting around chatting, no flirting with Dana, no staring at me when you think I'm not looking."
    bs "No te quedes ahí sentado charlando, no coquetees con Dana, no me mires fijamente cuando creas que no te veo."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:16
translate spanish mills1_1e9feafd:

    # bs "You've been slacking off around here and I'm tired of it."
    bs "Has estado holgazaneando por aquí y estoy harta de ello."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:17
translate spanish mills1_bd4fb3de:

    # bs "So clean up this office. I want it cleaner than it has ever been."
    bs "Así que limpia esta oficina. La quiero más limpia que nunca."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:18
translate spanish mills1_27d60d0e:

    # bs "I want to see you on your knees, getting all the dust out of the corners and polishing every inch of this place."
    bs "Quiero verte de rodillas, quitando todo el polvo de las esquinas y puliendo cada centímetro de este lugar."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:21
translate spanish mills1_f9906f0b:

    # "I grab my supplies and immediately go to work."
    "Cojo mis utensilios y me pongo a trabajar de inmediato."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:23
translate spanish mills1_641fb955:

    # bs "I already told you what you did wrong. You're lazy and I'm tired of you taking advantage of my kind nature."
    bs "Ya te he dicho lo que has hecho mal. Eres un vago y estoy harta de que te aproveches de mi bondad."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:25
translate spanish mills1_d41d8cd9:

    # voice 'voices/mills_nowgettowork1.mp3'
    voice 'voices/mills_nowgettowork1.mp3'

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:26
translate spanish mills1_af024200:

    # bs "Now get to work."
    bs "Ahora ponte a trabajar."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:29
translate spanish mills1_602e4e0a:

    # bs "Oh is it?"
    bs "¿Ah, sí?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:30
translate spanish mills1_5e887178:

    # bs "Is it bullshit?"
    bs "¿Es una tontería?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:31
translate spanish mills1_8273c1c7:

    # bs "What I think is bullshit is my paid intern talking back to me when I told him to perform a job."
    bs "Lo que yo creo que es una tontería es que mi becario remunerado me responda cuando le digo que haga un trabajo."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:32
translate spanish mills1_f88c2e68:

    # bs "Do you want me to fire you?"
    bs "¿Quieres que te despida?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:33
translate spanish mills1_a4adeba2:

    # "I think about it for a moment. I don't want to be treated like this, but I also need the money and am not sure if I'd be able to get another job easily."
    "Lo pienso un momento. No quiero que me traten así, pero también necesito el dinero y no estoy seguro de si podría conseguir otro trabajo fácilmente."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:34
translate spanish mills1_e842297d:

    # "Especially one where I get a free car out of the deal."
    "Especialmente uno en el que me regalen un coche."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:35
translate spanish mills1_9abd97c5:

    # pc "No ma'am."
    pc "No, señora."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:36
translate spanish mills1_0f684137:

    # bs "Then quit your back-talk and get to work."
    bs "Pues deja de contestarme y ponte a trabajar."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:38
translate spanish mills1_196ecdb4:

    # "I get to work cleaning everything, scrubbing every surface in the place, dusting the corners like she had said."
    "Me pongo a limpiarlo todo, fregando cada superficie del local, quitando el polvo de las esquinas tal y como ella me había dicho."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:40
translate spanish mills1_014d684e:

    # "I'm not sure that she is actually getting any work done while I am cleaning."
    "No estoy seguro de que ella esté haciendo realmente nada mientras yo limpio."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:41
translate spanish mills1_04589ea8:

    # "To me, it seems like she just sits there and watches me the whole time."
    "A mí me parece que se limita a sentarse ahí y mirarme todo el rato."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:42
translate spanish mills1_e02d88e1:

    # bs "Be sure you get that spot over there."
    bs "Asegúrate de limpiar bien esa zona de ahí."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:43
translate spanish mills1_6b79327c:

    # bs "If there's a single bit of dirt left over there later, I'm going to be very upset, [pcname]."
    bs "Si más tarde queda ni una sola mota de suciedad ahí, me voy a enfadar mucho, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:44
translate spanish mills1_27eb9444:

    # "I work like that for four hours, non-stop, until the office is closed and it is time to go home."
    "Trabajo así durante cuatro horas, sin parar, hasta que cierran la oficina y llega la hora de irme a casa."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:46
translate spanish mills1_e2dee895:

    # bs "Alright, stud, you can stop."
    bs "Muy bien, guapo, ya puedes parar."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:47
translate spanish mills1_53e9c55a:

    # bs "Stand up."
    bs "Levántate."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:51
translate spanish mills1_d41d8cd9_1:

    # voice 'voices/mills_didgoodwork.mp3'
    voice 'voices/mills_didgoodwork.mp3'

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:52
translate spanish mills1_2ca78f08:

    # bs "You did good work today."
    bs "Hoy has hecho un buen trabajo."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:53
translate spanish mills1_fe3292c7:

    # bs "Honestly, you do good work most days."
    bs "Sinceramente, casi siempre haces un buen trabajo."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:54
translate spanish mills1_a79bb6dc:

    # bs "I was in a bit of a bad mood earlier and took it out on you a little."
    bs "Antes estaba un poco de mal humor y me desquité un poco contigo."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:55
translate spanish mills1_cfb2e357:

    # bs "Sorry about that."
    bs "Lo siento."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:56
translate spanish mills1_be77b030:

    # bs "But seeing you on your knees working your ass off for me definitely made me feel better."
    bs "Pero verte de rodillas, dejándote la piel por mí, sin duda me ha hecho sentir mejor."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:58
translate spanish mills1_d41d8cd9_2:

    # voice 'voices/mills_thankyou2.mp3'
    voice 'voices/mills_thankyou2.mp3'

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:59
translate spanish mills1_66fe2ea0:

    # bs "Thank you for that."
    bs "Gracias por eso."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:60
translate spanish mills1_aa5ddb1f:

    # bs "Anyway, go on home. Thanks for working so hard today."
    bs "En fin, vete a casa. Gracias por trabajar tan duro hoy."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:61
translate spanish mills1_1ca80c77:

    # pc "Yes, ma'am."
    pc "Sí, señora."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:63
translate spanish mills1_1f470382:

    # "I leave her office and head down to the lobby."
    "Salgo de su oficina y me dirijo al vestíbulo."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:64
translate spanish mills1_f1b20649:

    # "Dana had already left. I hadn't even seen her all day after work started."
    "Dana ya se había ido. Ni siquiera la había visto en todo el día desde que empezó la jornada."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:65
translate spanish mills1_880f4fbb:

    # "Mrs. Mills had just wanted to see me on the floor. She seems to like that feeling of domination."
    "La señora Mills solo quería verme en el suelo. Parece que le gusta esa sensación de dominación."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:69
translate spanish mills1_94c66083:

    # "I have to admit, having her dominate me like that is pretty fucking hot."
    "Tengo que admitir que dejar que me domine así es jodidamente excitante."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:70
translate spanish mills1_947d9cb0:

    # "I wonder how far she would take it."
    "Me pregunto hasta dónde llegaría."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:73
translate spanish mills1_c7f17ec1:

    # "I don't like this at all. I don't want anything to do with her."
    "No me gusta nada esto. No quiero tener nada que ver con ella."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills1.rpy:74
translate spanish mills1_1180df5a:

    # "This isn't going to go any further."
    "Esto no va a ir más allá."

